        <mxCell id="kZJG9KBWsuVOy66hwry9-88" parent="kZJG9KBWsuVOy66hwry9-27" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;align=left;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;Company_identification can be any number that&#39;s max 10 digits that can be used to identify the company by bank(you), but usually it&#39;s:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;Company_identification = &quot;1&quot; + Company FEIN (9 digits)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;So:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;FEIN =&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 999111999&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;Company id = 1999111999&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
